"hallo", "gr[üu][ßs]", "grue[sß]", "hey", "hiho", german -> "Hallo mein Freund.", "Seid gegrüßt."

"how are you" -> "I'm fine, thanks. And you?"
"wie geht dir", "wie geht euch" -> "Mir geht es gut, danke. Und Euch?"
"who" -> "I am %NPCNAME. I help all people who are new to Illarion."
"wer" -> "Ich bin %NPCNAME. Ich helfe allen Leuten, die neu in Illarion sind."
"my name", "I am", "I'm" -> "Nice to meet you. My name is %NPCNAME."
"mein name", "ich bin" -> "Schön Euch zu treffen. Mein Name ist %NPCNAME."
"what sell", "what buy" -> "I am not a trader."
"was kauf" -> "Ich bin kein Händler."
"bye", "farewell", "be well" -> "Farewell.", "Be well.", "Good bye."
"auf bald", "bis bald", "leb wohl", "tschue[sß]", "tsch[uü][sß]" -> "Auf bald.", "Bis bald.", "Macht's gut.", "Lebt wohl."

